#Text=Q :
#Text=How could Brampton further itself in attracting corporate investment ?
#Text=A :
#Text=Of course , if the council shows an effective and efficient municipal management , it would be a strong showcase to attract corporate investors in Brampton .
#Text=This attraction is definitely paramount to ensure the economic development of the city and also the wellbeing of bramptonians who will be providing their expertise to these businesses .

#Text=To ensure the efficiency of such attraction , we much encourage corporate investment by providing to these investors a window of tax break for a define period of time ; establish competitive municipal tax rate which by itself would lure many investors ; organize showcase sessions , invite investors and publicize the millions reasons why their investments are worth being done in Brampton .
#Text=We must definitely use the fast growth of the city and the strong base of skilled and professional workers present in Brampton as a huge incentive for investment .
#Text=Q :
#Text=Why have you chosen to involve yourself in the political process ?
#Text=A :
#Text=I believe I have what it takes to bring hope and energy in Bramptonians life .
#Text=I do believe I have the vision that would help Brampton to distinguish itself among other municipalities in this twenty first century .
#Text=I strongly believe that I can turn our diversity into a huge strength and force that would propel Brampton into a respectable level .
#Text=I think Brampton , as a multi-ethnic and multi cultural city has what it takes to be a Canada model .
#Text=I do have what Brampton need to achieve it .
#Text=I am young , dynamic and resolute to bring the necessary change .
#Text=Brampton needs change ; Brampton council needs new faces .
#Text=I am involved in this political process because I would be the incarnation of the change and I would bring the energy that Brampton need to solve all pending issues .
#Text=Q :
#Text=What does Brampton mean to you ?
#Text=A :
#Text=My involvement in this political process is a proof of what Brampton means to me .
#Text=I have called Brampton home for many years now .
#Text=In front of the pending issues of our municipality , there is nothing else I could have done but to get involve , to instigate and to bring a new vision .

#Text=Instead of complaining or criticizing , there is a better way to make Brampton a better place to live in : it goes through my involvement in this political process , through what I bring to the table as ideas and it shows how much I love and adore this city .
#Text=I never would have decided to stay aside and wait for the miracle to happen .
#Text=I am bringing with me the miracle and I am sure that would serve the purpose and the interests of Bramptonians .
#Text=I am working hard to achieve these goals because Brampton means a lot to me .
